name: Miss K8
description: '''Kateryna Kremko''' ({{langx|uk|Катерина Кремко}}, born 18 June 1981), known professionally as '''Miss K8''', is a Ukrainian [[hardcore (electronic dance music genre)|hardcore]] DJ and producer. She has played at music festivals such as [[Defqon.1 Festival|Defqon.1]] and [[Masters of Hardcore]], gaining recognition for her performances. In 2019, Kateryna took some time off due to pregnancy.
